THANK YOU FOR DOWNLOADING BECONTENT. 

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTION
************************

To install your beContent website is very easy, first at all you need 
the following

	* PHP4.*
	* MySQL
	
then you need to 

1. create a MySQL database.

2. Customize the database information in the "include/config.inc.php" 
   configuration file. Please note, you may provide more than one host 
   installation, for instance your development and deployment hosts, 
   respectively.
   
3. Provide the administrator information.

Enjoy.
   